page.title: 13Trees
page.content: There are lots of trees in our area.There are Holly trees,Sycamore trees (which are also known as The Great Maple).Fir trees and Oak trees are also here. Fir trees have many different names.Two of them are The Spruce and The Douglas Fir,which are different kinds of fir trees. There are some trees which are not so popular in this area.For instance there are Locast trees in the forests.Also there are Lilac trees as well as Beech trees along the roads. Some of the most popular trees in the area are the Horse Chestnut trees and Apple trees.
